Yugi ad iffeɣ waṭṭan-agi.
Aṭṭan-agi yessenquqel akk ddunit.
Aṭas n temsal i d-ibeggen waṭṭan-agi.
Aṭas n leεyub i d-ifḍeḥ waṭṭan-agi.
Acimi i ugin kra takmamt?
Acimi tezgiḍ tettcukkuḍ?
Acimi tezgam tettcukkum?
Aṭas i iɣilen belli lmut tennulfa-d s waṭṭan-agi.
Am umerkanti am yigellil, yiwen ur t-iqal waṭṭan-agi.
A ziɣ ulac!
A ziɣ ulac deg wemdan!
